      "file_path": "kubernetes/aai/components/aai-modelloader/values.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 31,
      "line": 94,
      "message": "We do not need to change it, Sylvain asked me the same question too.\n\nIn fact, for some reason I get an error message stating that port 30229 is already in use.\nAs a result, aai modelloader will fail to load.\n\nI switched to 30299 in order to pass this error and ensure aai-modelloader is up.\n\nBut this will be reverted before merge as I suspect the issue to be specific to the environment where I perform my tests.",
